      "verse": "13:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 71.632,
      "end": 78.273,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will give children unto them to be their princes, and babes shall rule over them.",
      "verse": "13:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 78.953,
      "end": 81.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the people shall be oppressed,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 81.362,
      "end": 82.755,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "every one by another,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 82.935,
      "end": 85.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and every one by his neighbor;",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 85.391,
      "end": 89.431,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the child shall behave himself proudly against the ancient,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 89.611,
      "end": 92.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the base against the honorable.",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 92.577,
      "end": 107.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the people shall be oppressed, every one by another, and every one by his neighbour: neighbor; the child shall behave himself proudly against the ancient, and the base against the honourable. honorable.",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 107.978,
      "end": 112.622,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "When a man shall take hold of his brother of the house of his father,",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 112.802,
      "end": 114.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall say:",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 114.375,
      "end": 117.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou hast clothing, be thou our ruler,",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 117.434,
      "end": 123.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and let not this ruin come under thy hand\u2014",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 123.93,
      "end": 137.769,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "When a man shall take hold of his brother of the house of his father, saying, and shall say: Thou hast clothing, be thou our ruler, and let not this ruin be come under thy hand--",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 138.449,
      "end": 140.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "In that day shall he swear, saying:",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 140.951,
      "end": 142.716,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will not be a healer;",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 142.896,
      "end": 146.379,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for in my house there is neither bread nor clothing;",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 146.559,
      "end": 148.974,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "make me not a ruler of the people.",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 149.154,
      "end": 160.95,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "In that day shall he swear, saying: I will not be an a healer; for in my house there is neither bread nor clothing; make me not a ruler of the people.",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 161.63,
      "end": 163.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For Jerusalem is ruined,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 163.946,
      "end": 165.664,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Judah is fallen,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 165.844,
      "end": 167.702,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because their tongues",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 167.882,
      "end": 170.761,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their doings have been against the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 170.941,
      "end": 173.774,
