      "type": "line",
      "text": "Moreover, the Lord saith: Because the daughters of Zion are haughty, and walk with stretched forth stretched-forth necks and wanton eyes, walking and mincing as they go, and making a tinkling with their feet--",
      "verse": "13:16",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
