      "type": "line",
      "text": "baldness;",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 476.939,
      "end": 478.982,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and instead of a stomacher,",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 479.162,
      "end": 480.973,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a girding of sackcloth;",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 481.153,
      "end": 483.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "burning instead of beauty.",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 483.376,
      "end": 500.466,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass, that instead of sweet smell there shall be stink; and instead of a girdle, a rent; and instead of well set hair, baldness; and instead of a stomacher, a girding of sackcloth; and burning instead of beauty.",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 501.146,
      "end": 503.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thy men shall fall by the sword",
      "verse": "13:25",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 503.88,
      "end": 505.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thy mighty in the war.",
      "verse": "13:25",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 506.103,
      "end": 509.911,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thy men shall fall by the sword and thy mighty in the war.",
      "verse": "13:25",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 510.591,
      "end": 513.517,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And her gates shall lament and mourn;",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 513.697,
      "end": 519.038,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she shall be desolate,",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 519.218,
      "end": 521.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall sit upon the ground.",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 521.395,
      "end": 528.779,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And her gates shall lament and mourn; and she being shall be desolate, and shall sit upon the ground.",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 117
    }
  ]
